{"word":"πῶς 1","slug":"πῶς 1","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n92010\" key=\"pw=s1\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">πῶς</orth>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ion.\">Ion.</a></gram> </gramGrp> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">κῶς</orth>, interrog. <pos opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"pos\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Adv.\">Adv.</a></pos> of Manner, <sense id=\"n92010.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">how?</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:123\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.123</biblScope></bibl>, etc.; sts. to express displeasure, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:26\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.26</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg004.perseus-grc1:391\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ OT\">OT</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">391</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg006.perseus-grc1:1031\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ph.\">Ph.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1031</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg001.perseus-grc1:192\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tr.\">Tr.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">192</biblScope> </bibl>; to express astonishment or doubt, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">π. εἶπας</foreign>; <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekL